	<p>This BabyFolio Journey you are embarking on is both rewarding and challenging. We promise that as a result of this 5 day program, you will begin to better know your baby--  watching and noticing at deeper levels. Try it out, experiment and explore climbing into the mind of your child. You will experience the joy of getting to know their world reading more from their daily behaviors. </p>
 
	<p>So take a deep breath, smile, and commit to give it a try for at least these 5 days.</p>

	<p>We'll be there to support you each step of the way and we know you will be pleased with the results.</p>

	<p class="blue">Annie<br/>
	  Community Manager
